Six samples of how to use the ChartJS library with Charts on bars, lines, pizza, donut, radar and horizontal bars.

link for more graphic samples
https://www.chartjs.org/samples/latest/

link to the ChartJS project in github
https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js

link to the ChartJS documentation
https://www.chartjs.org/docs/latest/

link to the ChartJS documentation how to use
https://www.chartjs.org/docs/latest/getting-started/usage.html

Sites where the data I used was extracted
http://www.worldpopdata.org
https://ourworldindata.org/
